# AI Fortune Teller

Before non-trivial work, read [MEMORY.md](../../MEMORY.md) for current state, recent fixes, and changelog.

Architecture and API details live in [PLAN.md](../../PLAN.md). Do not duplicate them in edits unless the spec changed.

## Non-negotiables

- **Stack:** Vite 8, React 19, Tailwind CSS v4 — no TypeScript or new deps without user approval.
- **API:** Only `src/api/fortuneTeller.js` calls APIVerve (`GET https://api.apiverve.com/v1/fortuneteller`, header `X-API-Key` from `VITE_API_KEY`).
- **No backend** unless explicitly requested.
- **Never commit** `.env` or secrets.
- **Components** do not `fetch` directly — use `useFortune` + `fetchFortune`.
- **Categories:** Import `VALID_CATEGORIES` from `src/api/fortuneTeller.js`.

## After completing work

Update [MEMORY.md](../../MEMORY.md): **Current state**, **Changelog** (date + summary), and **Known issues** if applicable.

## Style

Minimal diffs; use Tailwind utilities and `@theme` tokens from `index.css`; preserve accessibility (`aria-live`, form labels, `role="alert"` on errors). Use `motion-reduce:` variants on animations.
